algorithms.html:
When asked to <dfn class="dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel" data-dfn-type="dfn" data-export="" data-lt="generate a counter|generate a counter representation" id="generate-a-counter" role="button" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0">generate a counter representation</dfn>
	using a particular counter style for a particular counter value,
	follow these steps:

steps.html:
For the informal styles,
		if the counter value is between ten and nineteen,
		remove the tens digit (leave the digit marker).

For each group with an odd index (as given in the second step),
			except groups which originally had a value of zero,
			append ፻ U+137B.

For each group with an even index (as given in the second step),
			except the group with index 0,
			append ፼ U+137C.
